{% include navbar-eot.haml %}
%section.background-eot
  %section.main-jumbotron.eot
    .text.bg-eot-main
      %h1.eot.hide Edushifts On Tour
      %h2.eot.hide Presente

  %section.eot.about-eot#about
    .container
      .row
        .col-sm-6
          %h2.text-right-art
            EDUshifts
            %br/
            OnTour 
            %br>/
            Executive 2018
            %br/
            %span.big
              Brasil
              %span

        .col-sm-6.border-left-dotted
          %h2.eot
            %span.text-green Ready to step out
            %br/
            of our reality?
          %hr.border-black
          :markdown
            Our society is undergoing an intense transformation. A growing number of citizens is challenging the status quo and adopting sustainable ways of living, working and learning.

            We invite conscious decision makers and enablers to explore and suppoort cutting edge solutions while experiencing the dynamic ecosystem of Brazil. EDUshiftsOnTour Executive - this journey will transform the way you collaborate and create impact.


  %section.eot.details-eot#details
    .container
      .row
        .col-md-6.col-sm-12
          %h2.eot
            What is in there for
            %span.text-green you
            ?
          :markdown
            STEP OUT of your demanding environment. Are you chasing a new world while being caught in old paradigms and minsets? Learn how to create impact beyond traditional paths and investments.

            EXPERIENCE how to set up exponetial projects while taking care of your personal needs. Learn to use your superpowers and adapt to a new reality.

            COLABORATE with a new generation of thought leaders and upcoming game changers. Follow your call and enjoy heartful and mindful relationships to yourself and people around you!

            GET TO KNOW Social Innovation projects and inspiring learning communities in two contrasting hotspots: the "Valley Wisdowm" Alto Paraiso and metropolitan São Paulo. The future is now!

        .col-md-6.col-sm-12
          %h2.eot
            %span.text-green INFORMATION
            &
            %span.text-green DETAILS
          :markdown
            **Dates:** 01.11 - 11.11.2018
            **Locations:** Rio de Janeiro and São Paulo.

            **Your investment** EUR 7.599 - EUR 9.599.*
            **Included in this lifetime adventure:**
            - Accommodation, Breakfast and Dinner, local transportation in Brazil for all group activities. __Not included__ : flights to Brazil.
            - Curated impact journey & deep personal learning experience. Topics: Transformation in Education. Social Innovation and Community building.

            *We use a Pay-it-Forward and Solidarity Economy Model for promising talents and social entrepreneurs will join the tour.*

        .col-md-6.col-sm-12
          %h2
            Ready for an
            %span.text-green Adventure of a lifetime
            ?
          Find out this experience is a food fit for you. Reach out for Phillipe Greier
          %span.text-orange.strong philippe@present-e.org

  %section.eot.details-eot#our-mission
    .container
      .row
        .col-md-6.col-sm-12
          %h2.eot 
            WHAT IS OUR
            %span.text-green MISSION
            ?
          :markdown
            We will create a documentary about the transformation in education in our society. Brazil has been a melting Pot for social movements and Progressive education.

            Join us and create a new reality. Let's tell a different story full of hope inspiring while setting up the foundation for a global movement!

        .col-md-6.col-sm-12
          %h2.eot Who We Are?
          :markdown
            Present is a non-profit foundation committed empower our society for a conscious evolution. Since 2011 we have been running EDUshiftsOnTour in multiple regions: Europe, Midddle East and South America. More information at
          %img.text-icon{src: 'assets/images/icons/web-icon.png'}
          %a.text-orange.bold{href: "www.present-e.org"} www.present-e.org
          %img.img-responsive.img-small{src: 'assets/images/present-logo.png'}

  %section.eot.destaque-img
    %img.img-responsive{src: 'assets/images/EDUshiftsOnTourX18.png', alt: 'pictures of the group during past eduontour'}

  %section.eot.book-authors#team
    .container
      .text-center
        %h2.eot
          Get to know our
          %span.text-green team
        
      .row
      {% for team in site.data.eot_team %}
        .author.text-center.col-md-6
          %img.img-square(src="assets/images/team/{{ team.name | slugify }}.jpg" width='150' height='150')
          %h5.orange-color {{ team.name }}
          :markdown
            {{ team.bio }}

          {% if team.twitter %}
          %a(href="{{ team.twitter }}")
            %img.icon.orange-color(src="assets/images/icons/twitter-orange.svg")
          {% endif %}

          {% if team.linkedin %}
          %a(href="{{ team.linkedin }}")
            %img.icon.orange-color(src="assets/images/icons/linkedin-orange.svg")
          {% endif %}

        {% endfor %}

  %section.eot.get-news
    .container
      %h2.text-center Get news in your mailbox
      .row
        .col-sm-4.col-sm-offset-4
          %form(action="//world.us16.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=4fb16c76a798800052ceeadfe&amp;id=84eb5b8ebd" method="post" id="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" name="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" target="_blank" novalidate="")

            .form-group
              %input.form-control{name: "EMAIL", placeholder: "you@example.com", type: "email", value: ""}
              %div{"aria-hidden" => "true", style: "position: absolute; left: -5000px;"}
            .form-group
              %input.btn.btn-primary.form-control{name: "subscribe", type: "submit", value: "Subscribe now"}

  %section.get-in-touch#contact
    .container
      .row
        .col-sm-5
          %h4 Get in touch with us

          %p
            %img{src: "assets/images/EDUshifts-logo_onTour_full_blue-01-200x107.png", width: '200', alt: "EDUshifts on tour logo"}

          %p
            {% for social_network in site.data.social_networks %}
            %a{href: "{{ social_network[1] }}", target: "_blank"}
              %img.icon-small(src="assets/images/icons/{{ social_network[0] }}.svg")
            {% endfor %}

          %p
            %a{href: "mailto:ahoi@edushifts.world?subject=[book]edushifts"}
              %strong ahoi@edushifts.world

        .col-sm-7
          %iframe{allowfullscreen: "", frameborder: "0", height: "315", src: "https://www.youtube.com/embed/I77GLPqxPCk", width: "560"}

